    <!--
      Navigation shell. Owns the chrome once for the whole app: a NavigationView pane on wide
      layouts (desktop / web) and a bottom TabBar on narrow ones (phone). Responsive switching is
      driven by the Toolkit {utu:Responsive} extension on each property (not AdaptiveTrigger /
      VisualState) so it applies reliably to this navigation-injected page. The content region is
      left empty — Uno.Extensions Navigation injects the active route (Home / Plan / Progress / Profile).
    -->
